==Awards==
[[File:Carduelis-tristis-001.jpg|thumb|The [[American goldfinch]] is the official county bird of Howard County.&lt;ref name=&quot;howardcountymd.gov&quot;&gt;{{cite web|url=https://www.howardcountymd.gov/About-HoCo/County-Symbols|title=County Symbols|website=www.howardcountymd.gov}}&lt;/ref&gt;]]
Awards and recognitions achieved by Howard County or locations within it include the following:

* &quot;4th Richest County in America&quot;, Forbes Magazine, 2017. &lt;ref&gt;{{Cite web|title=4. Howard County, MD (Median household income: $110,224)|url=https://www.forbes.com/pictures/5963ed594bbe6f269f7f2e9d/4-howard-county-md-median/|access-date=2020-09-23|website=Forbes|language=en}}&lt;/ref&gt;
